<A>__{sam and suzy turn and walk out of the chapel tent holding hands. they do not smile. cousin ben, skotak, and the rest of the troop follow them with grave expressions on their faces. sam touches suzy's hair. suzy kisses sam's hand. they walk as a group through the camp.}
